(144, 'Inbound via Chandrika (Quivly) - 2026-02-28: Source: Chandrika Maheshwari (Quivly) forwarded to Cash on Feb 28, 2026. Chandrika says she''s been "super impressed with the product" - Quivly is a design partner. PITCH (from Shagun''s email Feb 27): "Engram is the brand brain for fast-scaling AI companies. As a company grows, brand and marketing context (how you position, how you respond to the market, what sounds like you) becomes impossible to transfer at scale. The faster you grow, the worse it gets. Engram makes brand intelligence institutional so it compounds as you scale instead of fragmenting. The system learns your taste, your context, and your decision-making, and turns it into something your whole team can use." STATUS: Live with design partners and a few early paying customers, all Seed-to-Series A AI companies. Planning to raise a pre-seed soon. FOUNDERS: 1. Shagun Ohri (CEO) - shagun@engramhq.com - 2x founder, 14+ years in brand and marketing - Most recently Director of Marketing at Together Fund working with Series A AI companies - Rahul''s concern: "background of hopping around quite a bit" - suggested checking with Subham at Together Fund 2. Siddhant Singh (CTO) - siddhant@engramhq.com - Previously built a generative media platform for enterprise (Volkswagen, J&J) - Scaled Flipkart Ads to $1B ARR - PRIOR Z47 HISTORY: Affinity shows email exchanges and meeting in Feb 2024 (last email: Feb 20, last event: Feb 8). Personal email: siddhant0204@gmail.com OPEN ITEMS: - Ca...')
